    <name>Machines: Wired For War</name>
    <summary>
        3D Real-Time Strategy video game from 1999 developed by Charybdis and released as free software by Night Dive Studios
    </summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            The application requires original game assets. In case of Flatpak installation the files (top-level `machines` directory) should be placed at ~/.var/app/io.github.wiredforwar.machines/data/.
            The final game data structure should include 'models', 'pdata', and 'sounds' in ~/.var/app/io.github.wiredforwar.machines/data/machines/.
        </p>
    </description>
